TimescaleDB alohida Alembic muhiti.

OLTP (alembic/) dan MUSTAQIL — TIMESCALE_URL ga ulanadi.
Faqat GPS/time-series migratsiyalari bu yerga tegishli.

Foydalanish:
  cd backend
  alembic -c alembic_timescale.ini upgrade head
  alembic -c alembic_timescale.ini current
  alembic -c alembic_timescale.ini history

alembic_version_timescale — alohida versiya jadval nomi
(OLTP alembic_version bilan to'qnashuv yo'q).
